Title : Isaac Van Alphen
Text : [[File:Isaac Van Alphen.jpg|thumbnail|right|Isaac Van Alphen]]
[[File:C. 1896 official In Dienst (On Service) postal stationery envelope to Isaac Van Alphen.jpg|thumbnail|right|Official "In Dienst" (On Service) postal stationery envelope to Isaac Van Alphen.]]
Dr. '''Isaac Van Alphen'''  was [[Postmaster General]] during the [[Transvaal Republic|Transvaal Second Republic]],<ref>"The Transvaal - A Challenge" by Alan Drysdall in ''[[Gibbons Stamp Monthly]]'', June 1997, pp. 47-49.</ref> appointed on April 1, 1885.

